  DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN

    These routines delete the character under the cursor; all characters to
    the right of the cursor on the same line are moved to the left one
    position and the last character on the line is filled with a blank. The
    cursor position does not change (after moving to y, x, if specified).
    (This does not imply use of the hardware delete character feature.)

